Sarbit Advisory Services Inc.Sarbit Advisory Services Inc. is a privately owned firm, based in Manitoba, Canada, that manages equity mutual funds for its clients. Based on its own research, the firm invests in U.S. companies it believes have strong fundamentals but are currently 
	undervalued. Sarbit Advisory Services follows a strict investment discipline that calls for extremely intensive research into companies before they invest in them. They are proud to say that they are one of a handful of investment firms in Canada to employ the 
	full-time analytical skills of a lawyer and investigative journalist, with an eye towards protecting and enhancing your investment. 
