  Add Some Punch	                 














Some simple advice as paraphrased from Warren Buffett.
An investor should act as though he had a lifetime decision card with just twenty punches on it.
With every investment decision his card is punched, and he has one fewer available for the rest of his life.
Choose wisely for good returns.
Make Sarbit your next punch.











        

